      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 10.499229001998897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "だってドーナツが好きなだけ食べれるんだよ？\nご機嫌に決まってるじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can eat all the donuts I want‚ right?\nOf course I’m in a good mood!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.302966382286765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 16.976530599594117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツのどんな所が好きなんだ？\nそりゃ美味しいけどさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you like about donuts?\nI mean‚ I know they taste good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.369525553629956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 21.36514739990235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　それを芽衣に聞いちゃう？\n芽衣、沢山語っちゃうよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You’re really going to ask me that?\nI’ll talk your ear off‚ given the chance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.82229036603656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 27.915147590637247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ここは人気店らしい。目の前には行列が出来ている）\n（いくら芽衣の話が長くても、順番までには終わるだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(This place is popular. There’s a line in front of us.)\n(She’ll finish explaining before we reach the front‚ for sure.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.34887002967298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 36.3062131881714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
