      "text": "芽衣がドーナツを好きな理由その一\n……食感！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reasons I love donuts! Number one!\n…The texture!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.70180347079322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 41.2629254341125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ふわふわもちもちで、口の中に広がるあの食感が\nなんとも言えないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So fluffy‚ so chewy‚ that feeling spreading in your mouth.\nIt’s indescribable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.59625876744589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "豆腐ドーナツとかオススメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I recommend tofu donuts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.87394799365793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 47.87394799365793
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
