      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 50.252360717199174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "二つの材料だけでサクっと作れるの\n魔法みたいにパーって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They only have two ingredients. Super easy to make.\nLike magic! Boom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.285694050532534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 55.87961110248364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、そうなのか\nその二つの材料って？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ I had no idea.\nWhat are the ingredients?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7777919581287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 60.65051802768502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "知らないの？　材料はね、絹ごし豆腐と\nホットケーキミックス。この二つだけで出来ちゃうの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t know? All you need is some silken tofu\nand hotcake mix. That’s it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 68.4171846943517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
