      "text": "大豆を使うからイソフラボンも入ってるし\n美容にもいいらしいよ。しかもカロリー控えめ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The soy means they contain isoflavones‚\nso they’re good for your looks! Low calorie too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.74439672564637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 76.09695802504021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "詳しいんだな。それだけ知ってるなら\n芽衣は美味しいドーナツを作れそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know a lot. I bet you could\nmake some delicious donuts yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.41098416670357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
