      "text": "芽衣の作るドーナツ？\n芽衣は食べる専門だし、知識と技術は別物だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make my own donuts?\nMy thing is eating. “Knowing” and “doing” are very different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.57849841344927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
