      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "違うかな？　うーん、まあ細かいことはいいや\nおしまい！　好きな理由その二に入りまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think? Well‚ who cares about such details!\nThat’s it for reason one! Moving on to reason two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.39070111317209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
